# =============================================================================
# FORGE MARCUS — screening config TEMPLATE (.env.example)
#
# HOW TO USE:
#   1. This is a template only. The REAL file next to it is  marcus.env
#   2. Copy this file:  cp marcus.env.example marcus.env  then edit values.
#   3. Restart the connector (or redeploy) so it reloads.
#
# Marcus is the wholesale lead-SCREENING agent. He reads a seller's GoHighLevel
# text thread + Scout's triage, then writes a SELLER SCREENING REPORT + call-prep
# notes + a lead-stage recommendation so the operator knows who to personally CALL.
#
# Marcus is NOT a closer: he never texts a seller, never makes an offer, never
# talks numbers (no ARV / MAO / price unless the seller already gave one), never
# writes a contract. Scout still owns triage scoring + tags + pipeline. Marcus
# only ADDS the deep qualification layer and proposes a stage for human approval.
#
# SAFETY:
#   This folder is a SIBLING of the web app ("forge rei/"), so it lives OUTSIDE
#   the web-served dir. Nothing here is reachable over HTTP. Keys stay private.
# =============================================================================

# --- Auto-screen behaviour ---------------------------------------------------
# When Scout flags a lead "asap", auto-generate a screening report so it's waiting
# (1 = on, 0 = off). On-demand "Re-screen" from the dashboard always works.
FORGE_SCREEN_AUTO=1

# Max seller messages pulled per thread when building a report (cost/rate guard).
FORGE_SCREEN_MSGS=20

# --- Self-improvement loop ---------------------------------------------------
# Auto self-improve Marcus's screening playbook after N new screenings…
FORGE_MARCUS_LEARN_EVERY=15
# …rate-limited to at most once every this-many minutes.
FORGE_MARCUS_LEARN_GAP_MIN=45

# --- Anthropic (Marcus's OWN Claude key) ------------------------------------
# Optional. Marcus's dedicated screening key. If unset, FALLS BACK to the shared
# wholesale Anthropic key (../marcus-wholesale-agent/config/ghl.env).
# MARCUS_ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...

# --- Obsidian brain (vault) -------------------------------------------------
# Optional override for the Agentic-OS Obsidian vault path. Marcus reads his
# learned playbook from <vault>/Skills/marcus-screening-playbook.md in addition
# to the local skills/marcus-screening-playbook.md in this folder.
# FORGE_VAULT=/Users/yg4st/Desktop/Agentic-OS/vault
